<li><a href="#delete-a-location-attribute-sub-resource">Delete location attribute sub resource</a></li>
</ol>
<h2 id='list-location'>List location</h2>
<ul>
<li><h3 id='list-all-non-retired-locations'>List all non-retired locations`.</h3>
<p>Quickly filter location with given query parameters.Returns a <code>404 Not Found</code> status if the location not exists. If the 
user not logged in to perform this action,a <code>401 Unauthorized</code> status returned.</p>
<h3 id='query-parameters'>Query Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td><em>q</em></td>
<td><code>Search Query</code></td>
<td>Display Name of Location object.</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table></li>
</ul>
<pre class="highlight shell_session"><code>GET /location?
q="amani"
</code></pre>
<ul>
<li><h3 id='list-location-by-uuid'>List location by UUID.</h3>
<p>Retrieve a location by its UUID. Returns a <code>404 Not Found</code> status if the location not exists. If the user not logged 
in to perform this action, a <code>401 Unauthorized</code> status returned.</p></li>
</ul>
<pre class="highlight shell_session"><code>GET /location/:target_location_uuid
</code></pre><h2 id='create-a-location'>Create a location</h2>
